				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="dablink">"Masudi" redirects here. For other uses, see <a href="Masudi_(disambiguation)" title="Masudi (disambiguation)">Masudi (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
<table class="infobox biography vcard" cellspacing="3" style="border-spacing: 3px; width:22em;">
<tr>
<th colspan="2" class="" style="text-align:center; font-size:125%; font-weight:bold;"><span class="honorific-prefix" style="font-size: small"><a href="Muslim" title="Muslim">Muslim</a> <a href="Scholar" title="Scholar" class="mw-redirect">scholar</a></span><br />
<span class="fn"><b>Abu al-Hasan Ali ibn al-Husayn al-Mas'udi</b></span></th>
</tr>
<tr class="">
<th scope="row" style="text-align:left;">Title</th>
<td class="" style=""><b>al-Mas'udi</b></td>
